Package contextualegonetwork

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Context  
    ContextualEgoNetwork
    This class implements a Contextual Ego Network, that is the conceptual model of our Heterogeneous Social Graph.
    CustomDeserializer<T>
    This abstract class is meant to be extended with a custom, programmer-defined serializer class that best adapts to the needs of the program that exploits the HELIOS library.
    Edge
    This class implements an edge of the Social Graph.
    Interaction
    This class implements a generic interaction between two entities in a context.
    Layer
    This class implements a layer of the Contextual Ego Network, that is a conceptual structure made of a context and its translation function.
    Node
    This class implements a node in the Social Graph, which is representative of a node in a particular layer of the HSG.
